    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"최수민 개발 블로그","siteUrl":"https://sumini.dev"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d2f1f505-187a-5914-a038-463b95f96515","excerpt":"상대 경로를 사용하면 package 구조가 깊어질 수록 파일 간의 관계를 파악하기 어려워지고, 파일 이동시 귀찮게 경로를 수정해야 합니다. 예시 절대 경로를 사용하면 depth와 상관 없이 일관되고 짧은 경로를 작성할 수 있으며, 파일 이동시에도 그대로 사용할 수 있습니다.…","html":"<p>상대 경로를 사용하면 package 구조가 깊어질 수록 파일 간의 관계를 파악하기 어려워지고, 파일 이동시 귀찮게 경로를 수정해야 합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>예시</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Space<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Line <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'../../../../../../../component/atoms'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">MIDDLE_GREY</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'../../../../../../../component/atoms/colors'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>절대 경로를 사용하면 depth와 상관 없이 일관되고 짧은 경로를 작성할 수 있으며, 파일 이동시에도 그대로 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Space<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Line <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@src/component/atoms'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">MIDDLE_GREY</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@src/component/atoms/colors'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"1-타입스크립트-컴파일러-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%9F%AC-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"1 타입스크립트 컴파일러 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 타입스크립트 컴파일러 설정</h2>\n<p>typescript compiler에게 <code class=\"language-text\">@src</code>가 루트 경로의 <code class=\"language-text\">src</code> 폴더 임을 알려줘야 합니다. 루트 경로의 <code class=\"language-text\">tsconfig.json</code> 파일을 수정하면 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"compilerOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    ...\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"baseUrl\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"paths\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"@src/*\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"src/*\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<center>tsconfig.json</center>\n<h2 id=\"2-babel-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-babel-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 babel 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Babel 설정</h2>\n<p>babel이 코드를 compile할 때, 절대 경로로 작성된 path를 이해하도록 설정을 추가해야합니다. 루트 경로의 <code class=\"language-text\">.babelrc</code> 파일을 수정하면 됩니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm i -D babel-plugin-module-resolver</code> 을 입력해 플러그인을 설치합니다.</li>\n<li>루트 경로의 <code class=\"language-text\">.babelrc</code> 파일에 다음 코드를 추가합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ...<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"plugins\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    ...<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">\"module-resolver\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"alias\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token property\">\"@src\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./src\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"ref\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ref\" aria-label=\"ref permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ref</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/module-resolution.html\">typescript - module resolution</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/home.html\">공식 문서</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">예시</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%9F%AC-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">1. 타입스크립트 컴파일러 설정</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-babel-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">2. Babel 설정</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#ref\">Ref</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/guide/003-react-typescript-absolute-import/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React+Typescript 절대경로 import 설정하기","date":"2020-09-18T03:03:10.169Z","tags":["react","typescript"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":2.027027027027027,"src":"/static/6ea3d05c93d1e53241406845c25302ea/f3583/ts-react.png","srcSet":"/static/6ea3d05c93d1e53241406845c25302ea/630fb/ts-react.png 300w,\n/static/6ea3d05c93d1e53241406845c25302ea/2a4de/ts-react.png 600w,\n/static/6ea3d05c93d1e53241406845c25302ea/f3583/ts-react.png 1200w,\n/static/6ea3d05c93d1e53241406845c25302ea/10bb3/ts-react.png 1330w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/guide/003-react-typescript-absolute-import/","previous":{"excerpt":"Next.js 개발환경에서 window object를 사용할 때, document is undefined, Cannot read innerWidth of undefined 등의 에러메세지를 마주할 때가 있다. Next.js…","fields":{"slug":"/issue/000-nextjs-window,document-is-not-defined/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-09-15T03:19:10.169Z","title":"Next.js \"window,document is not defined\" 해결하는 법","layout":"post","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"originalImg":"/static/bbc016fa1685c64a2b61da4817186d6c/3225f/nextjs.png"}}}}},"next":{"excerpt":"설치 styled-components를 설치합니다. : styled-components의 type definition 모듈입니다. (참고 : @types라이브러리란?)  : className에 해당 compone